Program: Outlook
Title: Daryl Hannah
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrw6
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Daryl Hannah talks about her impressions of Rwanda and filming undercover for a documentary on the trafficing of children in the sex trade. Also, the Egyptian born conjoined twin Manar Maged who has died aged two; Indian singer Seema Anil Sehgal; Chinese author Sun Shuyun retraces the Long March; Blook awards. Show less